# Medical Imaging & 3D Visualization Portfolio

This repository demonstrates workflows used in medical imaging analysis and 3D anatomical visualization.

The examples focus on interpreting medical scan data and generating visual models from imaging datasets.

## Skills Demonstrated

• Medical imaging visualization  
• CT and MRI scan interpretation concepts  
• Image segmentation techniques  
• 3D anatomical reconstruction  
• Visualization of volumetric datasets  

## Example Projects

### CT Scan Visualization
Visualization of computed tomography datasets to explore anatomical structures.

### Image Segmentation
Segmenting anatomical regions from medical imaging datasets.

### 3D Reconstruction
Generating 3D anatomical models from volumetric scan data.

## Tools Used

3D Slicer  
Medical imaging datasets  
Volumetric visualization techniques  

## Purpose

This repository demonstrates knowledge of medical imaging workflows and visualization methods relevant to biomedical research and AI training projects.
